      "span_text": "An accurate closed-form approximation of the ASEP over a log-normal fading channel has been derived for any practical dB spread values and various constellation sizes and types. First, using the approximation of Q(x) in [CITATION_1] and a simple linear approximation for f (x), we have obtained an expression P e that closely approximates P e for large values of I, L, and N ."
